flowchart TD
    %% Note versioning flow (snapshot + delta)
    A["note.content (current)"] -->|"initial create"| B["note.version_snapshot"]
    B -->|"update"| C["note.version_delta"]
    C -->|"apply deltas"| D["reconstructed content"]
    D --> E["restore note.content"]
    C -->|"threshold reached"| F["new note.version_snapshot"]
